      "instruction": "<p>Chop the <strong>chives </strong>finely</p><p>Dice the <strong>tomato<span class=\"text-danger\">[es]</span></strong></p><p>Dissolve the <strong>chicken stock mix</strong> in 50ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[100ml]<strong> </span>boiled water</strong></p>",
